{"tid":884953,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"王晶2019年賀歲片, 甄子丹主演","createTime":"2018-11-01T04:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T06:57:18.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dca8eb3d904e476c63b2d80c8ff3461678e9dc9f","tid":884953,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"王晶監製, 甄子丹主演, 谷垣健治導演既<strong>強國合拍片</strong>《肥龍過江》, 應會在2019新年檔期上映.   (谷垣健治係blog中證實了)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ameblo.jp/t-yoshiji/entry-12407581633.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fameblo.jp%2Ft-yoshiji%2Fentry-12407581633.html&d=uXNkVBNXjWnhZA1iHhmX7SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=bee40c97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ameblo.jp/t-yoshiji/entry-12407581633.html</a><br />\n<br />\nさて、今月の映画秘宝のコラムによると、「肥龍過江」の公開は来年の旧正月ごろになりそうだとか。"},{"pid":"9089ce8564f6dbb3d7b8767b8b872170b0a5719b","tid":884953,"uid":66839,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:06:08.000Z","msg":"唔好俾我估中<br />\n<br />\n最尾係肥螳螂大戰葉問"},{"pid":"5fa01483721d4e7d85dc72b1998f16e9c4c30ea9","tid":884953,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:07:41.000Z","msg":"王祖藍早收到風<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到賀歲片對手強勁，祖藍表示：「好似有林敏驄、彭浩翔、王晶、《喜劇之王2》，唔緊要，香港呢幾十年都冇一套本土嘅粵語歌舞片，我哋有一個好唔同嘅特色喺度。」"},{"pid":"d4d292fc6b49236c41420a5871f45e5e6ba2108a","tid":884953,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"睇個名都覺得會好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a7a195c21a3a7953dc94ec177f118d45e299c5","tid":884953,"uid":156652,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d4d292fc6b49236c41420a5871f45e5e6ba2108a","tid":884953,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"睇個名都覺得會好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"